
						<h3>Aon Interactive Marketing Internship</h3>
						<a href="web-design/aon-marketing/aicpa-newsletter/newsletter.htm" target="_blank"><img src="web-design/aon-marketing/images/aicpa.jpg" style="width:162px; height:200px; float:left; padding:12px 10px 0px 0px;" alt="AICPA e-Newsletter" /></a>
                        <p>In the summer of 2011, I interned at Aon Insurance, a Fortune 500 company, in Horsham, PA as an interactive marketing assistant. Responsibilities included executing interactive creative and communications initiatives in the web space. I worked on research for Web 2.0 Marketing strategies, email newsletter and promotion HTML design, ad banner and navigation designs, and search engine optimization. Much of my design and rsearch has been applied to the Aon and it's affiliate web sites.</p>
						<h4><a href="web-design/aon-marketing/aicpa-newsletter/newsletter.htm" target="_blank">AICPA e-Newsletter</a></h4>
						<p>For this project, I was given a past AICPA newsletter template and asked to redesign the email with updated images, including the stock photo, and the implementation of social media sharing.</p>
						<h4>ASAE Follow-Up Email: <a href="web-design/aon-marketing/asae-email/asae1.htm" target="_blank">Version 1</a> / <a href="web-design/aon-marketing/asae-email/asae2.htm" target="_blank">Version 2</a></h4>
                        <a href="web-design/aon-marketing/asae-email/asae1.htm" target="_blank"><img src="web-design/aon-marketing/images/asae01.jpg" style="width:162px; height:200px; float:right; padding:4px 0px 10px 0px;" alt="ASAE: Version 1" /></a>
						<a href="web-design/aon-marketing/asae-email/asae2.htm" target="_blank"><img src="web-design/aon-marketing/images/asae02.jpg" style="width:162px; height:200px; float:right; padding:4px 10px 10px 10px;" alt="ASAE: Version 2" /></a>
						<p>For this project, I was tasked with designing a follow-up email for those attendees to the ASAE Conference that opted-in to more information. Similarly to previous projects, I was provided with previous email designs and images to use in my design process.</p>
						<a href="web-design/aon-marketing/nso-webinar/webinar.htm" target="_blank"><img src="web-design/aon-marketing/images/nso-webinar.jpg" style="width:176px; height:200px; float:left; padding:0px 10px 10px 0px;" alt="NSO Webinar" /></a>
						<h4 style="margin-top:121px;"><a href="web-design/aon-marketing/nso-webinar/webinar.htm" target="_blank">NSO Webinar</a></h4>
						<p>For this project, I was tasked with designing a notification email for an upcoming seminar to send out to a previously opted-in email list. Similarly to previous projects, I was provided with previous email designs and images to use in my design process.</p>
						<a href="web-design/aon-marketing/nso-navbar/navbar.htm" target="_blank"><img src="web-design/aon-marketing/images/nso-navbar.jpg" style="width:300px; height:95px; float:right; padding:10px 0px 10px 10px;" alt="NSO Navbar" /></a>
                        <h4><a href="web-design/aon-marketing/nso-navbar/navbar.htm" target="_blank">NSO Navbar</a></h4>
						<p style="margin-top:20px;">For this project, I was tasked with redesigning the existing NSO navigation bars to include a third option section, Personal Insurance, in addition to the options of Professional Liability Insurance &amp; Risk Management Resources that fit in flawlessly with the site and previous bar designs.<br />
						<b>NOTE:</b> All JavaScript and CSS pages were taken from previous resources, with consent from Aon Insurance affiliates. I only edited the CSS pages.</p>
						<h4>ASPN Banner</h4>
						<p>For this project, I was tasked with designing a new ASPN banner to be included in Aon affiliate web sites. I was provides with previous ASPN banners for reference for my own design.</p>
