						<h4 style="margin-top:20px;">ICRC/NSO Banners</h4>
						<p>For this project, I was tasked with redesigning an ICRC and NSO banner to be included in Aon affiliate web sites. I was given instructions as to what changes and additions were needed for the new banners.</p>
